{"tid":1444654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我知大家無力感好重⋯","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:39:55.000Z","uid":252031,"like":147,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"49489aa241936e8e8dd9fc3b008dfb883e29a139","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"先唔好介意我係p牌仔第一次開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6月9號以嚟keep住有出去發夢<br />\n由100萬人到612第一次面對黑警開槍<br />\n200萬人到衝擊立法會<br />\n721鄉黑合作之後對香港嘅失望係前所未有嘅<br />\n呢段時間大家日日都幾場夢遊<br />\n但成效都係有限<br />\n睇住對方武力不停升級，而我地嘅手足就不停比人拉<br />\n我好明白大家無力感好重，但唔好忘記我地有6個手足因為呢場抗爭無咗條命<br />\n每次睇住手足比人拉都好心痛，但我唔會放棄，因為盧烈士嘅遺言一路提醒住我，我地香港人唔可以放棄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8vQpLE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8vQpLE.png&h=6ee91246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢場運動我地得返嬴同死兩條路，希望大家唔好再互相指責，一齊捻下我地當初講嘅<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非&mdash;deadline&mdash;行動升級</span></strong><br />\n係時候停一停，組織返一次大型和理非比前線抖下，理清目標，比時間文宣煲大721同武警入侵事件，set deadline否則行動升級，例如再次發動罷工<br />\n最後我想講，香港人我愛你地<br />\n五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b892fb1719ac11581bb2342a94473035662367a8","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"49489aa241936e8e8dd9fc3b008dfb883e29a139","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"先唔好介意我係p牌仔第一次開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6月9號以嚟keep住有出去發夢<br />\n由100萬人到612第一次面對黑警開槍<br />\n200萬人到衝擊立法會<br />\n721鄉黑合作之後對香港嘅失望係前所未有嘅<br />\n呢段時間大家日日都幾場夢遊<br />\n但成效都係有限<br />\n睇住對方武力不停升級，而我地嘅手足就不停比人拉<br />\n我好明白大家無力感好重，但唔好忘記我地有6個手足因為呢場抗爭無咗條命<br />\n每次睇住手足比人拉都好心痛，但我唔會放棄，因為盧烈士嘅遺言一路提醒住我，我地香港人唔可以放棄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8vQpLE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8vQpLE.png&h=6ee91246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢場運動我地得返嬴同死兩條路，希望大家唔好再互相指責，一齊捻下我地當初講嘅<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非&mdash;deadline&mdash;行動升級</span></strong><br />\n係時候停一停，組織返一次大型和理非比前線抖下，理清目標，比時間文宣煲大721同武警入侵事件，set deadline否則行動升級，例如再次發動罷工<br />\n最後我想講，香港人我愛你地<br />\n五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"原來我甩咗P牌，自推10下先"},{"pid":"1c11999f15c077157dbc65bebcb9cd34aa8ad247","tid":1444654,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"罷買啦"},{"pid":"b1ffd737877b2596554dbc9097622b525b468bdb","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"79dd0f3125c8f192ee67a8ed86633a3aaf63ba82","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"c332510877c5c54e43e2ec0b5d7df69a0d4b3647","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:01:51.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"3455fe7bfbd824d0e4971d7c3d661cb1d934ddc4","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"c8090f3d9498cac77c7b888560de9545b34602c2","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"5bbc1cc5787fb3dd9a763e88aaac358c0d58dbe1","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"c48c192efb