a-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/</a><br />\n<br />\n22:30 ,檢舉&quot;幫港出聲&quot;專頁,5分鐘後再檢舉多次<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilentmajorityhk%2F&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=40b30e07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家用 whatspp ,IG ,snapchat...等分享比朋友又好,口講又好,有Facebook既,應該要幫手檢舉!  記得係仇恨言論<br />\n<br />\n增加對家文宣成本,我地香港人唔會屈服同認輸,大家請盡量分享出去~每人分享比10至20個朋友,記得今晚10點開始Facebook 集體檢舉!"},{"pid":"a4a976cf17abe502d6cd113f6b4edd6f53ffe288","tid":1444654,"uid":285118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"我愛所有手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地一齊諗之後對策好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6a4f77fd5fee4d70d3aeba667efd7cfe06c7e6","tid":1444654,"uid":33857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"講得啱<br />\n係好無助但都要頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"72d52232e31107d25b061531ad6f37f573c60bdd","tid":1444654,"uid":278002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"推 多謝巴打提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要堅持呀各位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"3a550ae27bdb765aff984cf04d42f6c2e4c4a265","tid":1444654,"uid":266959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"冷靜冷靜以待時局變化！<br />\n香港不孤獨！冷靜點！<br />\n等一等其他人！<br />\n要同世界局勢配合，G20一單就好大威力！<br />\n一定會贏！"},{"pid":"da3447f675a0cbef28e74bfd33102792a52e8267","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"另外仲有d嘢想講好耐，我地依家對付嘅係腐敗嘅政權，千奇唔好覺得我地係企係正義嘅一方而有潔癖覺得一定唔可以做d乜一定要點點碟碟，因為現實社會正義嘅一方通常無好下場，我地做d乜歷史會還我地清白<br />\n依家無論前線做乜我地都唔會割，但都唔等於白白送人頭，希望大家回歸返和理非&mdash;死線&mdash;行動升級，而且目標要清晰，等大家可以行動一致d<br />\n絕對唔係想分化，呢幾日如果大家想快閃，要有快閃嘅陣形，唔好堆埋一齊因為驚散唔切，如果想衝嘅唔好佢地一出嚟就驚，我地人多近身搏擊我地有優勢<br />\n親眼係黃大仙見證，d人要堅守就算出大量催淚彈都唔會後退，後尾夜晚班狗想武力清場，成千人幾十秒就散曬，非常值得參考<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb592c8e43325dffebbbde47f070345002deea2","tid":1444654,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"講左死線之後行動升級幾多次"},{"pid":"96548701ac00abe4eff47fe51280bdc88929571b","tid":1444654,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4a976cf17abe502d6cd113f6b4edd6f53ffe288","tid":1444654,"uid":285118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"我愛所有手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地一齊諗之後對策好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"巴打，我地係一家人嚟，一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90442296fda2df76a1962c84be0ca8f2b662f6f","tid":1444654,"uid":114155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"對準721單野搞一次大遊行！"},{"pid":"703493e50d8c7e5b73c03fef661ce1607bf2abe6","tid":1444654,"uid":261872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"就快崩潰<br />\n個心勁痛~ <br />\n我己無1-2星期追得咁緊要~ <br />\n不過見到今日D畫面同資訊真係唔知講乜好<br />\n再係咁我驚會有情緒病"},{"pid":"1484993cb389ff0aaa4a283526c3325cfac4b4a9","tid":1444654,"uid":114155